org.unisens

Interface UnisensFactory


  • public interface UnisensFactory
    UnisensFactory is used to create all Objects of a unisens implementation, that have to be created directly (i.e not by a Unisens object).

      • createUnisens

        Unisens createUnisens(java.lang.String path)
               throws UnisensParseException
        Creates a new Unisens object. If path points to an existing unisens dataset, it is loaded. Else new unisens dataset is created.
        Parameters:
        path - path to existing or new unisens dataset
        Returns:
        Unisens object
        Throws:
        UnisensParseException
